  "version": "1.0",
  "_doc": "Curated phrases for v0 classification. A record counts as a complaint if its text contains any of `complaint_phrases`. Defection rhetoric is a separate parallel signal — labeled in the UI as rhetoric, not behavior. Update by hand; the whole corpus is reclassified on each update. The list undercounts on purpose — transparent over noisy. Trend matters more than absolute level.",
